title: Fishermans Bend development approval lacked infrastructure plans, Andrews Government report finds
text: Victoria's former planning minister approved the redevelopment of Fishermans Bend in Melbourne without ensuring there was proper infrastructure, a report commissioned by the State Government finds. ...
